<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: chopped anima stump -->
  <ChoppedStump_Anima.label>砍倒的生命之樹樁</ChoppedStump_Anima.label>
  <!-- EN: A stump left behind after an anima tree has been felled. The stump can be extracted but yields very little usable wood. Left outdoors, the stump will deteriorate in time. -->
  <ChoppedStump_Anima.description>一棵生命之樹倒下後剩下的樹樁。樹樁可以被採伐但只會產出很少可用的木材。樹樁在戶外一段時間便會自然分解。</ChoppedStump_Anima.description>
  
  <!-- EN: anima grass -->
  <Plant_GrassAnima.label>生命之草</Plant_GrassAnima.label>
  <!-- EN: A grass infused with luminous microorganisms. Tribal peoples find that anima grass grows around the base of an anima tree as they meditate. It seems to reflect some kind of strengthening of the tree's psychic power.\n\nOffworld scientists have tried to study the phenomenon, but the grass degenerates into normal plant matter when observed too closely.\n\nAnimals refuse eat anima grass. Tribal stories say this is done out of respect and fear. -->
  <Plant_GrassAnima.description>注入發光微生物的草。部落的人們發現，在冥想的過程中，生命之草會在生命之樹底下生長。似乎反映出樹木的心靈力量一定程度的增強。\n\n世界各地的科學加試圖研究這種現象，但是如果觀察的太近，草就會退化成一般的植物。\n\n動物不會食用生命之草。部落的故事說道，這是出於尊重和恐懼。</Plant_GrassAnima.description>
  
  <!-- EN: anima tree -->
  <Plant_TreeAnima.label>生命之樹</Plant_TreeAnima.label>
  <!-- EN: A rare tree with warm, skin-smooth bark and long iridescent leaves. Infused with bioluminescent micro-organisms, anima trees develop a unique form of psychic symbiosis with surrounding lifeforms, allowing them to grow in a wide variety of biomes.\n\nIf a person (psycaster or not) meditates near an anima tree, it will grow anima grass around its base. Once enough grass is grown, it becomes possible to carry out a psychic linking ritual with the tree and upgrade a person's psychic powers. Only tribal peoples know the secret of this ritual. Tribal psycasters are also able to draw psyfocus from anima trees while meditating to them.\n\nAnima trees' psychic properties are weakened if artificial structures are placed nearby. They refuse to be caged or studied, and must remain part of nature.\n\nMost tribes believe that anima trees are not simply trees, but are rather the physical extremities of a single world spirit. -->
  <Plant_TreeAnima.description>樹皮溫暖、光滑、有彩虹般長葉的稀有樹木。充滿發光微生物，生命之樹會與周遭的生命發展出獨特的精神共生行為，從而能夠在各種的生態系統中生長。\n\n如果一個人(不論是不是心靈能力者)在生命之樹附近冥想，都會在它底部周圍生長生命之草。一旦長出足夠的草，就可以與樹的心靈聯繫，提高人的心靈力量。只有部落的人們知道這儀式的祕密。部落的心靈能力者也可以在冥想的同時從生命之樹上獲得精神力。\n\n如果附近有建築物，生命之樹的心靈特性會被減弱。它們拒絕被圍封或被研究，而必須維持在大自然中。\n\n大多數的部落相信，生命之樹不僅是樹木，而是世界之靈的一個分支。</Plant_TreeAnima.description>
  <!-- EN: About: Anima tree linking -->
  <Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompPsylinkable.enoughPlantsLetterLabel>關於：生命之樹連結</Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompPsylinkable.enoughPlantsLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: The anima tree now has {0} anima grass around it. This is enough for a tribal person to begin their first linking ritual!\n\nThe linking ritual gives a level of psylink and the ability to use psychic powers. Upgrading to a higher level requires 20 grass.\n\nThe anima grass requirements for linking rituals to upgrade psycasters are:\n\n{1}\n\nNote: Only those with the nature focus type can meditate to or link with anima trees. You can see a person's focus types by looking at their info card with the 'i' button. -->
  <Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompPsylinkable.enoughPlantsLetterText>現在生命之樹周圍有{0}個生命之草。已足夠為部落人民開始他們第一個連結儀式！\n\n連結儀式賦予了一定程度的心靈連結以及使用心靈能力的力量。升級到更高等級需要20株草。\n\n透過連結儀式升級心靈能力者所需的生命之草要有：\n\n{1}\n\n注意：只有那些自然焦點類型的人才能冥想或連結生命之樹。你可以透過"i"按鈕來查看某人的資訊卡來查看他們的冥想焦點類型。</Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompPsylinkable.enoughPlantsLetterText>
  <!-- EN: The anima tree has died and emitted a disturbing psychic scream. -->
  <Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompGiveThoughtToAllMapPawnsOnDestroy.message>生命之樹已死亡，並發出令人不安的精神嚎叫</Plant_TreeAnima.comps.CompGiveThoughtToAllMapPawnsOnDestroy.message>
  
  <!-- EN: smashed anima stump -->
  <SmashedStump_Anima.label>粉碎的生命之樹樁</SmashedStump_Anima.label>
  <!-- EN: The remnants of an anima tree destroyed by damage. It's ugly. The stump can be extracted but yields very little usable wood. Left outdoors, the stump will deteriorate in time. -->
  <SmashedStump_Anima.description>一棵生命之樹受攻擊破壞後所留下的殘跡。不堪入目。樹樁可以被採伐但只會產出很少可用的木材。樹樁在戶外一段時間便會自然分解。</SmashedStump_Anima.description>
  
</LanguageData>